---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';

---

<div class="relative w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-[32px] border border-border-light  dark:border-primary/20 overflow-hidden shadow-2xl flex flex-col lg:flex-row">
  {/* Left Side: Exam Content */}
  <div class="flex-1 p-8 border-r border-border-light  dark:border-primary/20 bg-slate-50/50 dark:bg-slate-950/30">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-10">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white">利用导数研究不等式问题</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 font-mono mt-1">Exam ID: 2024-MATH-FINAL-01</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-right">
        <div class="text-4xl font-display font-black text-primary">88</div>
        <div class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Total Score</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      {/* Question 1 */}
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800/50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-border-light  dark:border-primary/20 shadow-sm">
        <div class="text-lg font-serif italic text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 mb-2">
          f'(e) = a + 1 + 1 = 3 =&gt; a = 1
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Question 2 */}
      <div class="bg-rose-50/30 dark:bg-rose-950/20 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-rose-100 dark:border-rose-900/40 relative">
        <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 flex items-center gap-1 text-rose-500 dark:text-rose-400 text-[10px] font-bold">
          <Icon name="lucide:alert-circle" class="w-3 h-3" /> Review
        </div>
        <div class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mb-4">2. (15分) 证明：当x&gt;1时，x - 1 - ln x &gt; 0</div>
        <div class="text-xl font-serif italic text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 space-y-2">
          <p>令 g(x) = x - 1 - ln x</p>
          <p>g'(x) = 1 - 1/x = (x-1)/x</p>
          <p>当 x &gt; 1 时, g'(x) &gt; 0</p>
          <p>∴ g(x) 在 (1, +∞) 单调递增</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Question 3 */}
      <div class="bg-emerald-50/30 dark:bg-emerald-950/20 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-emerald-100 dark:border-emerald-900/40 relative">
        <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 flex items-center gap-1 text-emerald-500 dark:text-emerald-400 text-[10px] font-bold">
          <Icon name="lucide:check-circle-2" class="w-3 h-3" /> Full Score
        </div>
        <div class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mb-4">3. (10分) 计算不定积分 ∫ x e^x dx</div>
        <div class="text-xl font-serif italic text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 space-y-2">
          <p>解：令 u = x, dv = e^x dx</p>
          <p>du = dx, v = e^x</p>
          <p>∴ ∫ x e^x dx = x e^x - ∫ e^x dx</p>
          <p>= x e^x - e^x + C</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {/* Right Side: AI Insights */}
  <div class="w-full lg:w-[380px] p-8 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 flex flex-col">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-10">
      <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary">
        <Icon name="lucide:zap" class="w-5 h-5" />
      </div>
      <h4 class="font-bold tracking-widest text-sm uppercase dark:text-slate-200">AI Insight Engine</h4>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-6 flex-1">
      {/* Insight 1 */}
      <div class="p-5 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-emerald-500 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/40">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
          <Icon name="lucide:check-circle-2" class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500 dark:text-emerald-400" />
          <span class="font-bold text-sm dark:text-slate-200">逻辑推导完整</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          准确求出切线斜率，并在 x=e 处正确计算导数值。逻辑清晰，步骤完整。
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* Insight 2 */}
      <div class="p-5 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-amber-500 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/40">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
          <Icon name="lucide:alert-circle" class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 dark:text-amber-400" />
          <span class="font-bold text-sm dark:text-slate-200">论证过程跳跃</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
          虽然结论正确，但 "单调递增" 推导过程缺乏关键步骤。建议补充 g(1)=0 的验证。
        </p>
        <div class="inline-block px-2 py-1 rounded bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/30 text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 text-[10px] font-bold">
          建议扣分: 0.5
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Mastery Stats */}
      <div class="pt-6 border-t border-border">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-6">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest">知识点掌握度</span>
          <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-primary bg-primary/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">HIGH</span>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div>
            <div class="flex justify-between text-xs mb-2">
              <span class="font-medium dark:text-slate-300">导数应用 (Derivatives)</span>
              <span class="font-bold dark:text-slate-200">95%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="h-1.5 w-full bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
              <div class="h-full bg-primary mastery-bar" style="width: 95%"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="flex justify-between text-xs mb-2">
              <span class="font-medium dark:text-slate-300">逻辑推理 (Logic)</span>
              <span class="font-bold dark:text-slate-200">82%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="h-1.5 w-full bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
              <div class="h-full bg-primary/60 mastery-bar" style="width: 82%"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <button class="py-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-900 dark:bg-white text-white dark:text-slate-900 text-xs font-bold">生成个性化作业</button>
      <button class="py-3 rounded-xl border border-border-light  dark:border-primary/20 text-xs font-bold hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-800 dark:text-slate-300 transition-colors">查看全班分析</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .mastery-bar {
    animation: mastery-grow 1s ease-out forwards;
    transform-origin: left;
    transform: scaleX(0);
  }

  @keyframes mastery-grow {
    to { transform: scaleX(1); }
  }
</style>
